---
By: Meister Eckhart
Locus:
  Page: 41
  Verse: 5
Tags:
  - Cause
---
The seed of God is in us. Given an intelligent farmer and a diligent
farmhand, it will thrive and grow up to God whose seed it is and,
accordingly, its fruit will be God-nature. Pear seeds grow into pear trees;
nut seeds into nut trees, and God- seed into God.
